Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sei disso.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ora, que rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:09.96,Sign3,,0,0,0,,{\clip(209.634,304,355.324,378)\t(0,189,\clip(209.634,304,639.427,381))\pos(420.019,356)}Zoologico da Cidade Fukuoka
